<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Account Deactivated - HTU LMS</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Nunito+Sans:ital,opsz,wght@0,6..12,200..1000;1,6..12,200..1000&family=Nunito:ital,wght@0,200..1000;1,200..1000&display=swap"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
    <style type="text/css">
      body {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        min-width: 100%;
        font-family: "Nunito Sans", sans-serif;
        font-size: 14px;
        line-height: 1.5;
        background-color: #f4f4f4;
        color: #222222;
      }

      a {
        color: #0070f3;
        text-decoration: none;
      }

      h1 {
        font-size: 16px;
        font-weight: 700;
        margin: 0;
        text-align: center;
      }

      h2 {
        font-size: 14px;
        font-weight: 600;
        margin-top: 20px;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
      }

      p {
        margin: 0 0 16px;
      }

      .email-wrapper {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        background-color: #ffffff;
        border-radius: 8px;
        overflow: hidden;
        box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      }

      .email-header {
        background-color: #007bff;
        padding: 5px;
        color: #ffffff;
        text-align: center;
        border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
      }

      .email-body {
        padding: 10px;
        font-size: 12px;
      }

      .email-footer {
        background-color: #f4f4f4;
        padding: 20px;
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #777;
      }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-wrapper">
        <div class="email-header">
            <h1>Your Account Has Been Deactivated</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="email-body">
            <p>Dear <%= fullname %>,</p>
            <p>
                We wanted to inform you that your HTU LMS account has been successfully deactivated as per your request.
            </p>
            <p>
                If this was not done by you or if you wish to reactivate your account, please contact us immediately.
            </p>
            <p>
                We appreciate your time with us, and if you have any further questions or need assistance, please do not hesitate to get in touch.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="email-footer">
            <p>
                If you have any questions, please do not hesitate to contact us at
                <a href="mailto:michaelkpantiramp@gmail.com">michaelkpantiramp@gmail.com</a>
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
